urls.description: Vestas is a leading offshore wind turbine manufacturer with 8 + GW of offshore wind installed to date. We are the preferred supplier for the 2.1 GW Empire Wind offshore project in New York as well as Atlantic Shores’ 1.5 GW offshore project in New Jersey.
